{
  "texts": [
    "Such a systematic approach will address the weakness in current HCAI practice, enabling us to promote HCAI practice further and deliver endto-end HCAI solutions.",
    "Both HCAI and STS practices are mutually reinforcing.",
    "This paper proposes the iSTS framework to extend traditional STS theory and guide the advances of HCAI practice, maximizing the contributions of the STS approach.",
    "The proposed iSTS framework, based on the emerging sociotechnical characteristics demanded by AI and the updated STS design principles, has addressed many issues in alignment with the insights of the previous studies [32], [35], [43], [44], [78], [81], [84], [85], [89], [98], [99], [100].",
    "Furthermore, this paper proposes the hHCAI approach to address the challenges in current HCAI practice driven by the iSTS framework."
  ]
}